description.en:
The community has officially TAKEN OVER $HIPPO - after the dev threw in the towel! The cutest $HIPPO on SUI is now powered by a full CTO. No cats, no dogs. Only $HIPPO, driven by the people, for the people! $HIPPO is ready to break out stronger than ever!

Su Deng is the cutest $HIPPO on SUI, bringing $HIPPO to the world of memes.

$HIPPO - No cats, no dogs Only hippo!

We are donating a % of our profits to wildlife needs across the world. Starting with support for Khao Kheow Open Zoo, the zoo that houses Moo Deng
